{"id": 4057, "title": "Ticket #4057: Remove PrivSep from the HTCondor code base", "description": "<blockquote>\nSadly, the amount of effort that goes into maintaining <span class=\"wiki\"><a href=\"wiki?p=PrivSep\" title=\"Priv Sep\">PrivSep</a></span> does not seem to be worth it.  No one outside of the UW appears to use it.  It has many separate code paths which lead to inconsistent behavior when using vs not using <span class=\"wiki\"><a href=\"wiki?p=PrivSep\" title=\"Priv Sep\">PrivSep</a></span>.  It is incompatible with other desirable features such as cgroups.  It requires HTCondor to be installed differently and started differently via init scripts.\n\n<p>As such, we are removing it from the code base to simplify things.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2014-Jan-22 15:32:09 by smoler:</em> <br/>\n\nIn the manual, all documentation for <span class=\"wiki\"><a href=\"wiki?p=PrivSep\" title=\"Priv Sep\">PrivSep</a></span> is commented out; it is not deleted.\n\n<p>This documentation is not yet completed:\n\n</p><p></p><ol>\n<li>A version history item is needed\n</li><li>The condor_root_switchboard needs its own separate documentation. It has none in the manual at all.  The only place it was mentioned was in the section on <span class=\"wiki\"><a href=\"wiki?p=PrivSep\" title=\"Priv Sep\">PrivSep</a></span>, which is no longer included.\n</li></ol>\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2019-Nov-21 16:31:07 by tim:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>CODE REVIEW:</strong> Zach verbally approved these changes.\n\n<p>No docs needed. Unsupported for some time now.</p></blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6259\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6259'); return false;\" title=\"Remove condor_root_switchboard from the release\">#6259</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nRemove condor_root_switchboard from the release</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Oct-21 09:31</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/60e19ac4136811f35fbd14892b1e023fdf6bc012\">[58216]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4057\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4057'); return false;\" title=\"Remove PrivSep from the HTCondor code base\">#4057</a></span>) Remove <span class=\"wiki\"><a href=\"wiki?p=PrivSep\" title=\"Priv Sep\">PrivSep</a></span>  (By Tim Theisen )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2014-Jul-10 11:39</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/c584451094a47845ed19f9110acffeb446f1f695\">[40599]</a></span>: found 2 more references to <span class=\"wiki\"><a href=\"wiki?p=PrivSep\" title=\"Priv Sep\">PrivSep</a></span> in the manual. Gone now. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4057\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4057'); return false;\" title=\"Remove PrivSep from the HTCondor code base\">#4057</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2014-Jan-22 15:24</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-